# ALM v10.7 Validated Commands

## 1. Directory Structure Setup
(Ensure this runs before dataset generation)
`mkdir -p data/raw/speech data/raw/environment`

## 2. Generate Dataset & Extract Neural Features
(Produces cached `embeddings.npy` and `labels.npy`. Use at least 500-1000 samples for robustness!)
`python -m training.dataset_builder --num_samples 1000`

## 3. Train Fusion & Scene Context Network
`python -m training.train --epochs 50 --batch_size 32`

## 4. Run Unified Validation Pipeline (Terminal)
(Runs the end-to-end logic test without the UI)
`python main.py`

## 5. Launch Gradio Frontend
(Interactive UI for audio testing)
`python application/app.py`
